        jLabel2.setText("<html>SInce Actual Physical Memory is much smaller than virtual memory ,page faults may happen.In Case of page fault,Operating System  might have to replace one of the existing pages with newly needed page.Different page replacement algorithms suggest,different ways to decide which page to replace.The target for all algorithms is to reduce the number of page faults.</html>");
